OL,3,CWomen to spend 10m hours in summer
OL,4,Cfestival toilet queues, research
OL,5,Csuggests
OL,7,FWomen will waste an estimated 10
OL,8,Fmillion hours queueing for toilets at
OL,9,Ffestivals this summer, according the
OL,10,FBristol start-up that created the UK's
OL,11,Ffirst women's urinals.
OL,13,FDubbed the "female fun tax", these 10
OL,14,Fmillion hours are equivalent to 14
OL,15,Flifetimes or more than the work hours
OL,16,Fneeded to build the Empire State
OL,17,FBuilding.
OL,26,@uD@LOUuD@[O]
