PN,43102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1777359931
OL,3,CWomen to spend 10m hours in summer
OL,4,Cfestival toilet queues, research
OL,5,Csuggests
OL,7,FAmber Probyn co-founded Peequal and
OL,8,Fdeveloped the toilets which are said
OL,9,Fto be three times faster than
OL,10,Ftraditional portable toilets.
OL,12,FThey have been used more than one
OL,13,Fmillion times since 2022, cutting
OL,14,Fqueues at dozens of events, from
OL,15,FGlastonbury and Shambala to Pride
OL,16,Fevents and Download Festival.
OL,18,FThe organisations research shows that
OL,19,Fwomen on average queue for an hour per
OL,20,Fday at festivals.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1777359931
OL,3,CWomen to spend 10m hours in summer
OL,4,Cfestival toilet queues, research
OL,5,Csuggests
OL,7,FThey said that UK Music estimates that
OL,8,F6.5 million people attended music
OL,9,Ffestivals in 2022.
OL,11,FAnd assuming 50% of festival-goers are
OL,12,Fwomen, and the average festival length
OL,13,Fis three days, then that creates
OL,14,F9,750,000 hours spent in queues
OL,16,F"We've found the average woman queues
OL,17,Ffor more than an hour every day at
OL,18,Ffestivals. This female fun tax simply
OL,19,Fshould not exist in 2026," Ms Probyn
OL,20,Fsaid.
OL,26,@xD@AOU{D@ZO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
