FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1777359931
OL,3,CWomen to spend 10m hours in summer
OL,4,Cfestival toilet queues, research
OL,5,Csuggests
OL,7,F"These women should be out enjoying
OL,8,Fthe amazing events they paid to
OL,9,Fattend, not missing the headliner
OL,10,Fwhile they queue."
OL,12,FAt Sunday's TCS London Marathon,
OL,13,FPeequal unveiled its next generation
OL,14,Fof women's urinals ` its most
OL,15,Fsustainable, private and easiest to
OL,16,Fuse yet.
OL,18,FThe new urinals were developed after
OL,19,Ftwo years of research with women,
OL,20,Ffestival managers, cleaning staff and
OL,21,Fhaulage companies.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@RO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
