FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1777359931
OL,3,CWomen to spend 10m hours in summer
OL,4,Cfestival toilet queues, research
OL,5,Csuggests
OL,7,FThe urinals' flatpack, tessellating
OL,8,Fdesign means 56 urinals fit on one 44-
OL,9,Ftonne lorry.
OL,11,F"Our next-generation urinals will get
OL,12,Fwomen out of queues and back to the
OL,13,Fevents they love, all while making
OL,14,Fevents more sustainable," Ms Probyn
OL,15,Fadded.
OL,17,F"This summer, let's end the female fun
OL,18,Ftax."
OL,26,@sD@AOUvD@YO]yD@AOUzD@EO]
